# B2 — pip-compile INPUT (top-level runtime deps). The pinned + hashed lock is
# `requirements.lock`, generated from this file by `.github/workflows/lockfile.yml` running
# `pip-compile --generate-hashes` inside python:3.12-slim (the prod interpreter) — never on a dev box,
# so the resolved wheels always match production. Edit deps HERE; regenerate the lock via that workflow.
#
# This single lock covers the API image AND the test gate: the data service's runtime deps
# (services/data/requirements.txt) are a strict subset of the ones below, so they need no separate lock.

